snippet: Guatemalan police have detained seven alleged migrant smugglers who were part of a network that reached to the Mexico-U.S. border....

headline.print_headline: Guatemala Police Nab 7 Alleged Migrant Smugglers
headline.main: Guatemala Police Nab 7 Alleged Migrant Smugglers

lead_paragraph: Guatemalan police have detained seven alleged migrant smugglers who were part of a network that reached to the Mexico-U.S. border.
